      <h2>Post Wedding Brunch</h2>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3>Location:</h3><p>Battery Park Slip 6</p>
      <h3>Time:</h3><p>Sunday May 29, 2016 at 9:30 am - 12:15 pm</p>
      <h3>Attire:</h3><p>Casual to Smart Casual</p>
      <p>
        Please join us for brunch on the New York Water Taxi as we cruise around the sights of Lower Manhattan including the Statue of Liberty, Brooklyn Bridge, and Freedom Tower. Please arrive at the pier by 9:30 at the latest to embark on the vessel. A part of the boat is enclosed so there will be protection from inclement weather. 
      </p>
    </p>
