      <h2>New York Bus Tour</h2>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h3>Pickup Location:</h3><p>Battery Park Slip 6</p>
      <h3>Dropoff Location:</h3><p>Drop off Downtown Marriott</p>
      <h3>Time:</h3><p>Sunday May 29, 2016 at 12:15 - 4:15 pm</p>
      <h3>Attire:</h3><p>Casual to Smart Casual</p>
      Please join us for a tour of Downtown and Uptown Manhattan on a double decker bus. The tour will feature a tour guide from City Sightseeing and cover the Big Apple’s highlights. If you’ve seen Manhattan a thousand times from the ground or never seen it all, the tour will offer a different perspective with family and friends. Please note the bus will not make stops except for one bathroom break. The top section of the bus is not enclosed and inclement weather may require umbrellas or ponchos.
    </p>
